name: No Sugar Please/No Allergies
what_you_do: Oonagh Williams is a Food Allergy Coach who provides demystifying, educating and practical advice for food allergies.
who_you_serve: Oonagh serves audiences both large and small in a variety of different settings and contexts.
offering: Oonagh offers a great experience both on stage and off stage for event planners. She is known for being informative, interactive and fun.
signature_programs: Oonagh's well-regarded talks include 'The Power of Food', 'Best Medicine, Worst Poison', and 'How To Cook, So They Will Eat'.
business_focus: Oonagh provides demystifying, educating and practical advice for food allergies.
